@startuml 资源与环境管理时序图

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam participantFontSize 13
skinparam noteFontSize 11

actor 用户 as User
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "EnvironmentController" as EC
participant "AssetRegistry" as AR
participant "ResourceMonitor" as RM
participant "SnapshotManager" as SM
participant "TwinSyncService" as TSS

User -> Frontend : 选择场景模板并提交初始化请求
Frontend -> EC : init_environment(scenario_id, config)
EC -> AR : get_scenario_template(scenario_id)
AR --> EC : 返回场景配置
EC -> EC : 装载知识库、绑定向量索引、加载模型
EC -> RM : check_service_health()
RM --> EC : 返回服务状态列表
EC -> SM : create_snapshot(env_id, "初始基线")
SM --> EC : 返回 snapshot_id
EC -> TSS : sync_env_status(env_id)
TSS -> Frontend : WebSocket推送环境状态
EC --> Frontend : 返回初始化结果
Frontend --> User : 展示环境实例及资源监控

@enduml
